<section class="content-body">
  <div class="title">Download Desktop App</div>
  <div class="description">
    The desktop app is to allow a local code workspace to synchronize with a Codio box.
    Units/Projects from the <a href="/docs/dashboard/student/myclassroom">Classroom dashboard</a>
    and <a href="/docs/dashboard/student/myfirstproject">My Projects</a> area can be connected.
    A Codio account is required.<br/>
    To download the desktop app to install to your local machine select the appropriate OS (Tablet/Mobile devices are not supported).<br/>
    For more information, <a href="/docs/dashboard/desktopapp">click here</a>
  </div>
  <div class="download-block">
    <div class="item">
      <div class="os">Mac OS X</div>
      <%= link_to 'Download', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/codio-desktop-builds/Codio.dmg', class: 'button button-main button-rounded', target: '_blank', alt: 'MacOS Desktop App' %>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="os">Windows</div>
      <%= link_to 'Download', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/codio-desktop-builds/Codio.exe', class: 'button button-main button-rounded', target: '_blank', alt: 'Windows Desktop App' %>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="os">Linux</div>
      <%= link_to 'Download', 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/codio-desktop-builds/Codio-amd64.AppImage', class: 'button button-main button-rounded', target: '_blank', alt: 'Linux Desktop App' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>